      "text": "create:  support + PMs ship code too\nreview:  shared planning + review space\ngovern:  policy, evals, audit by default\nroles:   new -> AI product manager\nmetric:  outcomes, not seats or LOC", "originalText": "create:  support + PMs ship code too\nreview:  shared planning + review space\ngovern:  policy, evals, audit by default\nroles:   new -> AI product manager\nmetric:  outcomes, not seats or LOC",
